<div class="description">
    <h3>Description</h3>

    <div class="body">
        <p>If you define a route with a module + controller, zend_navigation_page_mvc cant recognize it as active. For instance if you create a  route with module Foo and controller Bar, and then create a page with that module + controller it won't register in active breadcrumbs. If I <em>do</em> specify the default action parameter of index then it does work correctly. Trivial but a user may not be using a route param called action</p>

